}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Alternate models of GWF-3E31, 3E33, 2E31, 2E32, 2E33 and WU-150. Devices are assumed to be identical to the GWF-3A3x models.
[http://www.ogemray.com/en/default.asp?id=1074 Product page for the GWF-3A32] <gallery> File:3E32.JPG|Picture of the GWF-3A32 / GWF-3E32 </gallery>[[Has images::external| ]] [http://www.ogemray.com/en/default.asp?id=1073 Product page for the GWF-3A31] <gallery> File:GWF-3A31.jpg|Black 3A31 File:3a31-3.jpg|another 3A31 File:3a31-2.jpg|Red 3A31 File:3a31-1.jpg|White 3A31 </gallery>
The 3A3T and 3A2T are not explicitly listed as models in the FCC reports, but may share the same board.
[http://www.ogemray.com/en/default.asp?id=1047 Product page for the GWF-3A3T]
"RoHS", "3E", and "Ver 1.2" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
<gallery> File:GWF-3A3T.jpg|GWF-3A3T shot </gallery> [http://www.ogemray.com/en/default.asp?id=1046 Product page for the GWF-3A2T] <gallery> File:GWF-3A2T.jpg|GWF-3A2T shot </gallery>
